snippet.title: The Thundermans Family Says a Final Goodbye 😢 | Nick
snippet.description:
The Thunderman family always manages to get out of trouble… but in this clip from the FINAL episode of the series, it doesn’t look like they will be so lucky.

Warning: This video is super emotional! May cause wet eyes. 😢

Catch more of The Thundermans on Nick!
